sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Користувач
    participant App as Flutter app
    participant ApiService
    participant API as FastAPI auth routes
    participant Security as security.py
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Local as SharedPreferences

    User->>App: Вводить username/password
    App->>ApiService: login(username, password)
    ApiService->>API: POST /token
    API->>DB: select User by username
    API->>Security: verify_password()
    Security-->>API: password valid
    API->>Security: create_access_token()
    API-->>ApiService: access_token, token_type
    ApiService->>Local: save auth_token
    ApiService->>API: GET /users/me
    API->>Security: get_current_user()
    Security->>DB: load User by JWT sub
    API-->>ApiService: UserBase
    ApiService->>Local: cache current user
    ApiService-->>App: logged in

    Note over App,ApiService: Startup auto-login
    App->>ApiService: tryAutoLogin()
    ApiService->>Local: read auth_token
    ApiService->>API: POST /refresh
    API->>Security: get_current_user()
    API->>Security: create_access_token()
    API-->>ApiService: refreshed token
    ApiService->>Local: replace auth_token
